<h2>Dependencies and prerequisites</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Android 2.1 (API Level 7) or higher</li>
  <li><a href="{@docRoot}tools/extras/support-library.html">Support Library</a></li>
</ul>

<h2>Try it out</h2>

